":0},"title":"Hadith on Fiqh: Excellence in Islam requires understanding","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: It was said to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhich people are the most noble?'' The Prophet said, \u201cThe most noble to Allah are the most righteous.\u201d They said, \u201cThat is not what we are asking about.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe most noble of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2011,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/27\/dua-sneezing-hamd-kul-hal\/","url_meta":{"origin":221,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Praise Allah in all situations after sneezing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Nafi\u2019 reported: A man sneezed beside Ibn Umar, saying, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah and peace be upon the Messenger of Allah!\u201d Ibn Umar said, \"I also say all praise is due to Allah and peace be upon the Messenger of Allah, but this is not what the Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7283,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/29\/prophets-righteous-severely-tested\/","url_meta":{"origin":221,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trials: The Prophets, righteous most severely tested","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa'd ibn Abi Waqqas reporte