wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32904,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/muruah-deen-aql-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":221,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Masculinity: Manhood in religion, reason, character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe nobility of a man is in his religion, his manhood is in his intellect, and his honor is in his character.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8575 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/07\/best-deen-easiest\/","url_meta":{"origin":221,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Moderation: Best of your religion is the easiest","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mihjan ibn al-Adra\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said three times, \u201cVerily, the best of your religion is the easiest of it.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 20349 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u0650\u062d\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u062f\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0639\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u